<plot>Join Nancy in Canada's Icicle Creek Lodge and find the White Wolf. Someone is sabotaging the Inn and you have to find out who. Join Nancy in her adventure to find the culprit and reveal the reason for the wolf's being there. You can question all of the guests and get insights into their lives, while gaining clues at the same time. You even get to be the chef and cook the meals! Skate and ice fish in this compelling adventure in Canada (not the North Pole or in igloos). Enjoy the game!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?389301</url></doc>
